data.description: Welcome to this breathtakingly fully remodeled two-bedroom, two-bathroom home, where modern elegance meets comfort. Freshly painted inside and out with a chic, contemporary palette, this home is a visual delight. The brand-new double-pane windows not only enhance the aesthetics but also ensure energy efficiency. Step inside to an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living room to the kitchen, adorned with new flooring that adds a touch of sophistication. The heart of this home, the kitchen, is equipped with high-end stainless steel appliances, sleek white shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, and a spectacular tile backsplash that's sure to impress your guests. Both bathrooms have been designed with style in mind, featuring designer elements and recessed lighting that create a spa-like atmosphere. Comfort is guaranteed year-round with a full central A/C and heating system. For your peace of mind, the home includes a brand-new septic tank, ensuring hassle-free living. The private backyard is a serene retreat, perfect for relaxation, recovery, and stargazing, making it an ideal space to unwind after a long day. Located just minutes from shopping, restaurants, and the majestic Joshua Tree National Park, this home offers the perfect balance of tranquility and convenience.
